        "timestamp": "2023-04-06 17:22:20.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-2\n\nOn testing this, I think I missed something in the initial analysis - for the arguments to the custom function we dont know what the argument types are. It would not be valid to assume the argument types are the same as the type of the property being set. Therefore we should not restrict the properties available under get_property to the same type as the property being set, and similarly for the other functions",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
